Currently this skill support smart plugs. If you have any problems, please contact us at hleyf@hle-1879.cn. 

Xiao He offers the most comprehensive voice controlled smart home experience with Alex. Control your home lighting and other devices handsfree. Just say it, Xiao He will obey.

Here's a step by step guide:
(1).Download our "Xiao He" app in Google Play or IOS App Store;
(2).Launch the app and register a new account(or Login if you're already registered);
(3).Turn on Home Linking devices and connect them with "Xiao He" app;
(4).IMPORTANT：You can rename the devices Home Linking APP. So you you rename
a smart bulb"Livingroom Light", then Echo will get that same name after discovered the devices in Step 9;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or IOS APP store, and connect
Echo with "Alexa" APP
(6). Search the Alexa Skill director for "Xiao He";
(7). Click Enable skill of "Xiao He", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page.
(8).Talk to Echo "Alexa, discover devices". Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.
